.title Help: OA&M Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The OA&M (Operations, Administration, and Maintenance)
package provides a character-based interface for performing
administrative tasks.

If you install this package, you must also install the Advanced
Commands package.  After installing the OA&M package use
Extra_Admin in Admin_Tools to access the OA&M features.

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
